9911,"uid":35375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T02:07:29.000Z","msg":"響香港撈極都撈唔起, 香港人唔欣賞佢, 咁大陸人會, 咪返大陸囉."},{"pid":"84b35ee2cf3a02bdc278e58286324fe23e6b0ddc","tid":779911,"uid":129221,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"86b760a60f478def00dc1993438650f33d8c51df","tid":779911,"uid":77959,"like":116,"dislike":1,"score":115,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T18:40:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>把聲零辨識度又冇個人風格，唱功又唔係話好好，唔明點解可以紅到，支那人品味真係 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>見的士陳都係支拿紅到就知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>香港人唔要嘅垃圾掟上大陸就會紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n例子:蝗祖藍，angelababy</blockquote>香港人要嘅大陸唔會紅<br />\n例子︰唯唯, 呀Bob, 坤哥, 吳若希<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港人幾時要佢哋"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T02:10:31.000Z","msg":"躝啦 你唔要我要"},{"pid":"d6a077d7b268224da46fbdfc92afee8484119367","tid":779911,"uid":64884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T02:13:12.000Z","msg":"國語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n蝗語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b411e70ed89633078374109defb988c20003c418","tid":779911,"uid":184592,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T02:15:42.000Z","msg":"聽完一次未必想聽第二次<br />\n<br />\n但今次又係香港歌手鄰國先紅得起，反映幾樣嘢：<br />\n1. 鄰國觀眾群大，而且會睇電視<br />\n2. 電視節質素有影響，節目符合国民口味，多人睇就可以造星（TVB節目差，冇人睇，所以本地音滲透度底）"},{"pid":"785f7a53b27cef659a6b96a3a713a2c50783bb01","tid":779911,"uid":59602,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"12e9717